{"title":"京都四韵","authors":["查干"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":12,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"京都四韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"查干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春　潇潇夜雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄色的迎春花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿然摇曳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗窗外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛然飘洒潇潇京都夜雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"护城河南岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见有渔器一上一下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那老翁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟把几代残梦削作鱼漂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而后凝神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一浮一沉地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"审视"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏　远处钟声荡漾而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偌大的京都"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躺于树下闲摇竹椅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风　真是太热了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吻于脸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆圆的似是铜板烫伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一杯凉茶下去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦清凉了许多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而远处钟声荡漾而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听来音色有变"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心似有异样感觉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是不好梳理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋　莲桥有残叶飘落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙里偷闲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一种生存方式"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踽踽独行并非心陷绝境"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过莲桥时魂有些颤栗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美　竟然会如此残落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一改往日的艳丽和潇洒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而小小青蛙蹲于莲叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似哲人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口吐寓言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬　飘雪铺开一张宣纸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轮声已息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四野静寂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立交桥头灯火阑珊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活大概太疲累"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪　静静地飘落下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺开上苍的一张宣纸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁来挥如椽之笔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涂一枝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新梅"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}